    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>整数倍</strong> \\to 对余数设状态，考虑同余最短路。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对当前的数 $S$ 做 ×10 或 +1 两种操作来建立出度，出度为 2，实现<strong>图的松弛</strong>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>转化</strong>：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "操作1：<code>x * 10</code> （数位和 +0，边权为 0）",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "操作2：<code>x + 1</code> （数位和 +1，边权为 1）",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "这题将问题转化为了 <strong>Dijkstra</strong> 在跑最短路的问题。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "struct node {\n\tint yu, sum;\n\tbool operator<(const node& a)const {\n\t\treturn a.sum < sum;\n\t}\n};\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint k; cin >> k;\n\tvar dis = vector<int>(k, INF);\n\tvar Q = priority_queue<node>();\n\tdis[1] = 1;\n\tQ.push({ 1,1 });\n\twhile (Q.size()) {\n\t\tvar[now, d] = Q.top();\n\t\tQ.pop();\n\t\tif (d > dis[now])continue;\n\n\t\tint to = now * 10 % k;\n\t\tint w = 0;\n\t\tif (dis[to] > dis[now] + w) {\n\t\t\tdis[to] = dis[now] + w;\n\t\t\tQ.push({ to,dis[to] });\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tto = (now + 1) % k;\n\t\tw = 1;\n\t\tif (dis[to] > dis[now] + w) {\n\t\t\tdis[to] = dis[now] + w;\n\t\t\tQ.push({ to,dis[to] });\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout << dis[0] << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
